Advanced Recon & Subdomain Enumeration Tool for Bug Bounty Hunters

GhostScan is a powerful Python-based automated reconnaissance tool designed for bug bounty hunters, penetration testers, and cybersecurity students.
It performs subdomain enumeration, port scanning, directory discovery, WHOIS lookups, and more â€” all automated in one script.

