ğŸ› ï¸ Installation
1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/0xDEADVrm/Automated-Bug-Hunter.git
cd GhostScan

2. Install Python Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Install System Dependencies (IMPORTANT)
Ubuntu/Kali Linux:
sudo apt install nmap wkhtmltopdf

â–¶ï¸ Usage

Run the tool like this:

python3 ghostscan.py -d example.com

Options
Flag	Description
-d	Target domain
-o	Save results to file
-w	Custom wordlist
--threads	Thread count
--no-dns	Disable DNS brute force
--simple	Minimal output

Example:

python3 ghostscan.py -d google.com --threads 50 -o report.txt

